value.title: Biden's inaugural committee hosting 'virtual parade across America' on Inauguration Day

value.title: Trump extends immigration restrictions, citing pandemic's impact on labor market
value.excerpt: President Donald Trump extended certain restrictions on legal immigration and on visas that allow immigrants to temporarily work in the United States on Thursday, just hours before those restrictions were set to lapse. Trump extended the restrictions through March 31, two months after he will leave office.
